# Put your custom Odoo modules in this folder (one subfolder per module).
# On push to main, the CI/CD pipeline syncs everything here to the server's
# /opt/odoo/addons (mounted into the Odoo container as /mnt/extra-addons)
# and restarts Odoo. Use the "Run workflow" button with a module list to
# run -u upgrades when you change views/data, not just Python.
